tonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 18, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104stn1665702655266.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/stn1665702655266.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/stn1665702655266.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"stn1665702655266\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      /lis\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Produce compile listings of ProcScript modules for components, application shells, menus, and global ProcScript.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"stn1665702655266__section_w2469ab1b5b1_w2470ab1b5_w2471ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"stn1665702655266__p_d150065e1_d150066e1_d150067e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/lis</span>{<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">1</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">2</code>}</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"stn1665702655266__section_w2472ab1b5b3_w2473ab1b5_w2474ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d322637e69\">\n                  \n Used With\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"stn1665702655266__d6347e22\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yqf1665702625882.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yqf1665702625882.html\" title=\"Compile application shells.\">/aps or /app</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"stn1665702655266__d6347e27\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"sww1665702625667.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sww1665702625667.html\" title=\"Compile all types of compilable main development objects, including components, modeled entities, and global objects.\">/all</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"stn1665702655266__d6347e32\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ifp1665702626096.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ifp1665702626096.html\" title=\"Compile all components, including server pages, HTML forms, forms, reports, services, entity services, and session services.\">/cpt</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"stn1665702655266__d6347e37\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ars1665702626915.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ars1665702626915.html\" title=\"Compile Uniface entity service components.\">/esv</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"stn1665702655266__d6347e42\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rtz1665702626248.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rtz1665702626248.html\" title=\"Compile dynamic server pages.\">/dsp</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"stn1665702655266__d6347e48\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fvm1665702627074.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fvm1665702627074.html\" title=\"Compile Uniface form components.\">/frm</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"stn1665702655266__d6347e53\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ixo1665702655853.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ixo1665702655853.html\" title=\"Compile global ProcScript and variables in a library.\">/lib</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"stn1665702655266__d6347e58\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lxo1665702656136.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lxo1665702656136.html\" title=\"Compile menu bars, menus, and menu items.\">/men</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"stn1665702655266__d6347e63\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kjb1665702652886.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kjb1665702652886.html\" title=\"Compile Uniface report components.\">/rpt</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"stn1665702655266__d6347e68\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"umc1665702653094.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/umc1665702653094.html\" title=\"Compile Uniface session service components.\">/ssv</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"stn1665702655266__d6347e73\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gku1665702653234.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gku1665702653234.html\" title=\"Compile Uniface service components.\">/svc</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"stn1665702655266__d6347e79\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"prm1665702626469.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/prm1665702626469.html\" title=\"Compile static server pages.\">/usp</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"stn1665702655266__section_w2475ab1b5b5_w2476ab1b5_w2477ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d322637e200\">\n                  \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"stn1665702655266__table_d18221e1_d18222e1_d18223e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Script Listing Level</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"stn1665702655266__table_d18221e1_d18222e1_d18223e1__entry__1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"stn1665702655266__table_d18221e1_d18222e1_d18223e1__entry__2\">Meaning</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"stn1665702655266__table_d18221e1_d18222e1_d18223e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">1</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"stn1665702655266__table_d18221e1_d18222e1_d18223e1__entry__2\">Generates a basic script listing with no\n                     precompiler directives.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"stn1665702655266__table_d18221e1_d18222e1_d18223e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">2</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"stn1665702655266__table_d18221e1_d18222e1_d18223e1__entry__2\">Generates a script listing that includes\n\t\t\t\t precompiler directives</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"stn1665702655266__section_w2478ab1b5b7_w2479ab1b5_w2480ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d322637e256\">\n                  \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"stn1665702655266__p_d150089e1_d150090e1_d150091e1\">If you do not specify a listing level, level 1 is used.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"stn1665702655266__p_d150092e1_d150093e1_d150094e1\">If the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/inf</span> sub-switch is used with <code class=\"ph codeph\">/lis=2</code>, the ProcScript listing includes additional compilation error, warning, and info messages.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vfm1665702655413.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Script Listings</a><p>A script listing is an ASCII file containing a concatenated list of all the compiled script in a component, application shell, menu, or global ProcScript. Separate script listings are generated for script in entity collection and entity occurrence triggers.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ybj1665702655557.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Generate and View Script Listings</a><p>You can configure Uniface to generate script listings by setting the $LISTING_LEVEL assignment setting or by using the /lis command line switch.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xio1665702655482.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$LISTING_LEVEL</a><p>Produce compile listings of ProcScript modules.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/czj1665702653450.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>/inf</a><p>Display the information listing plus warning and error messages when compiling.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532158\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532158\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "/lis Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 18, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 /lis Produce compile listings of ProcScript modules for components, application shells, menus, and global ProcScript. /lis { = 1 | 2 } Used With /aps or /app /all /cpt /esv /dsp /frm /lib /men /rpt /ssv /svc /usp Parameters Table 1. Script Listing Level Value Meaning 1 Generates a basic script listing with no precompiler directives. 2 Generates a script listing that includes precompiler directives Description If you do not specify a listing level, level 1 is used. If the /inf sub-switch is used with /lis=2 , the ProcScript listing includes additional compilation error, warning, and info messages. Related Links Script Listings A script listing is an ASCII file containing a concatenated list of all the compiled script in a component, application shell, menu, or global ProcScript. Separate script listings are generated for script in entity collection and entity occurrence triggers. Generate and View Script Listings You can configure Uniface to generate script listings by setting the $LISTING_LEVEL assignment setting or by using the /lis command line switch. $LISTING_LEVEL Produce compile listings of ProcScript modules. /inf Display the information listing plus warning and error messages when compiling. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}